text: Inske jitna chaapu insan apne kabhi nahi dekha hoga exam se pahele rona and phir exam me macha dena. Starting from robocon till now, we shared lots of memories, and it will be impossible for me to write each one of them. I still remember robocon nightouts and fhir class me jake dono so jate the kyuki class me to sab upar se jata tha. Exam ke time par ye library ko hi apna ghar bana lete the kyuki waha se CCD pass tha aur inhe CCD jane ka bahana chahiye bas ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚, abhi bhi teri 4-5 parties pending hai. The most dramatic thing was online Placement season, hamne code likhne se jayada ek dusre se chat ki hai and online test me bas dono ye hi puchte rahte the "hogaya" ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. Apan dono ne HSS ko chordkar laghbhag sare courses sath me kiye hai abhi tak. You were the first point of contact for any assignment and project, last din tak bhi assignment nahi hua to ek confidence tha bhai gangwar jugadwa dega. I have cherished each and every moment with you for the past 3 years. I donâ€™t think thereâ€™s anyone on this planet with your focus and dedication. Ese hi machate raho.

text: If you wish to describe Jay Gupta (tau) in a single phrase, i.e., Multi-Tasking with hanging. Aur hang hone ke baad ye aate the hamare pass reboot hone ke liye. text:
Tumhare sath to bhai hazaro memories hongi kyuki apne room se jayada time tumhare room me bitaya hai. Pura wing busy hota tha apan dono baithke movie ya youtube par time pass kar rahe hote the. Bas ek regret hai last me campus me mil nahi paaye.

Hamne jayada courses ek sath nahi kiye lekin jitne bhi kiye hai unme discussion karne me bahut maza aata aur DS me to endsem me bhi discussion kiya tha and ECO 201 ko kaise bhul sakte hai teeno ne milke ek sath kiya tha, wo baat alag hai ki meet par tum dono ka alag hi discussion chalta rahta tha ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. Aur bhai Jay par theories likhte rahna uska bhala hota rahega aur discuss karne me alag maja aayega.

Wing cricket me tumhari khatarnak sliding style of bowling, jiska ek do bar me bhi shikar hua hu, hamesha yaad rahegi. Tumhe Badminton me to occasionally hi hara pate the lekin maja bahut aata tha. 

Bas ab agli summers ka wait kar rahe tumhare sath trip par jane ke liye ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.

text:
Hi Sathvik
Chaar saal bahut sari merories share ki hai ab saari to nahi likh sakta lekin I will list a few of them. First year me yaad hai dono hi TA me kitni wahiyaad drawing banate the bas farak itna tha Tumhari branch Mech thi to tumhe aur sehna pada ğŸ˜‚, dono ko hi C ki umeed thi lekin pata nahi kaise B lag gaya. Aur bhi jitne courses kiye hai tumhare sath unme kafi maza aata tha, aur tumhari indepth knowledge ke to kya kahene. Bas PMI me meri baat maan lete aur drop na karte ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.

Be it trips, discussions on various profs (Modi ko prof kisne banaya), cricket, I have cherished every moment shared with you in the past four years. Bas ab ek trip plan karte hai, last time par mil nahi paye campus me, iska hamesha regret rahega. All the best for the future bro, I know you are destined for greatness ahead.

text:
Samagh nahi aa raha kaha se start karu likhne ko bahut kuch hai kyuki hamara safar IITK ke se pahele ka hai, from class 11th to IIT Kanpur lagbhag 6 saal ho gaye. Tumhari chapuness ke to kya kahene 11th se macha hi rahe ho you have not left any stone unturned be it bakchodi, extracurrics or academics. Iske baare me jayada nahi likhuga waise hi logo ne bahut likh dia hai. 

Robocon me tum nahi hote to MR1 ki halat bhi MR2 jaisi hoti. Abhi tak yaad hai wo last days of night outs to complete MR1. Sabse jayada dedicated tum hi the, ham bas aake roz ek hi kaam karte the timepass and khali dimaag me fhir mPID jaise idea aate hai ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. 

Fhir wing cricket ko kaise bhul sakte hai yaar jaha tak mughe yaad aa raha tumne mughe sabse jayada baar bold kiya hai. Last ke dino me jab sab campus me the tab ye bahut miss kiya maine. Hamne sath me courses bahut kam kiye hai Bajar batti and EE360 jisme fail hote hote A lag gaya ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚, lekin jab bhi kiye hai discussion karne me maja bahut aata tha, bajar batti endsem me to pata nahi kitni book padke gaye the. Ab aate hai Gupta Ji par isme jayada nahi likhunga kyuki ye endless topic of discussion hai, lekin trio call par algorithms discuss karna and Jay ki mauj lena ye hamesha yaad rahega and aage bhi continue rahega.

At the end tumhare jitna hardworking and passionate insan maine nahi dekha. Ese hi machate raho. Aaj lockdown thoda relax hua hai milte hai ek do din me waise Alwar me CP ke baad aaj tak nahi mile hai is streak ko tod dete hai ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.
author: Sabhay  Jain

text:
Chalo ab Tech guy of Wing ka memoir likhte hai, bhai abhi tak yaad hai tumhare se Linux dalwane ke liye line lagti thi. First year me course related hi discussion hota tha lekin second year se apna bond banna start hua and third year me to dono naman ke room par hi baithe rahte the, aur aajkal to laghbhag roz hi baat ho jati hai. Hope so ye continue rahe and ek din Bangalore me same room share kare ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.

Tum me chaar saal me kafi change aaya hai pahele thoda jayada hi self centered rahete the lekin ab sab chill hai ab sabki help kar dete ho. Especially placement kaise bhul sakta bhai tumhari wajah se hi itni shortlist aai thi. Hamne sath me courses bahut kam kiye hai lekin jab bhi kiye hai, discussion and projects karne me bahut maja aata tha be it SSP or image processing. SSP me to mughe abhi bhi yaad kaldi wala model roz girget ki tarah accuracy badal raha tha ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.

Mess me khana bekar bana ho to bahar se khana order karne ke liye hamesha ready rahete the, jis din nahi aa pata tha us din mango shake se hi kaam chalana padta tha. Tumhare sath Badminton, TT and cricket sab khela hai bas ye hi regret rahe gaya tha ki last time ye moments wapas cherish nahi kar paya. 

Dedicated and passionate to tum hamesha se hi ho bas ese hi machate raho and jaldi se Alwar aane ka plan banao.
author: Sabhay  Jain
